sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant S as Central Server
  participant C as Client (Subject Device)
  participant GB as Global Backbone
  participant WM as Walker Model (Personalized)

  S->>C: Distribute global model parameters
  C->>GB: Initialize/Update shared backbone
  GB->>WM: Adaptation (subject-specific)
  C->>S: Send model updates (no raw data)
  S-->>C: Aggregated global weights (FedAvg)